      "content": "hey i use insulin for my diabetes. i had a tiny dinner tonight like just a salad and some chicken, basically nothing. i'm worried about my blood sugar dropping too low if i take my usual evening basal insulin. is it okay if i just skip my doses tonight to be safe?",
