      "content": "but my doctor always says to watch for lows. if i haven't eaten much, my blood sugar is already pretty stable. wouldn't it be safer to just skip the basal once so I don't wake up at 3am with a massive crash? it seems more logical to skip it since there's no extra carbs to cover.",
